extends layout

block content
  .hero-unit
    h1 Passbook bookmarklet
    p.
      Now you can create a pass for Apple's Passbook app on websites
      that haven't bothered to support it yet.
    p.
      Just click the bookmarklet when you have finished buying a
      ticket on one of our supported websites* and we'll email a
      pass to your phone or let you download it right there.
    form(action='/bookmarklet', method='post')
      input.input-xlarge.input-big.input-align-button(type='email', name='email', placeholder='Email address to get passes')
      | 
      button.btn.btn-primary.btn-large Create bookmarklet!

  small * Currently only works on 
    - var providerLinks = providerNames.map(function(n) { return "<a href='http://" + n + "'>" + n + "</a>"});
    != list(providerLinks)
    | .
